        <short>Light automatic rifle.</short>
        <description>
            <para>
                A Belgium made light automatic rifle was first made in
                1953, and has been a popular weapon since then. It is
                classed as a <e>battle rifle</e>, making it more suited
                to longer range situations than <e>assault rifles</e>
                such as the M16 or AK47.
                A larger capacity magazine of 30 rounds do exist.
            </para>
        </description>

